\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

, we subtract 
\begin_inset Formula $2\times$
\end_inset

(row 
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

) from (row 
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

).
 To eliminate the 
\begin_inset Formula $(3,1)$
\end_inset

 entry of 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{21}A$
\end_inset

, we subtract 
\begin_inset Formula $2\times$
\end_inset

(row 
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

) from (row 
\begin_inset Formula $3$
\end_inset

).
 Finally, to eliminate the 
\begin_inset Formula $(3,2)$
\end_inset

 entry of 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{31}E_{21}A$
\end_inset

, we add 
\begin_inset Formula $p\times$
\end_inset

(row 
\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

) to (row 
\begin_inset Formula $3$
\end_inset

