 The sequence of transformations is
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{21}A=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
1 & 0 & 1\\
0 & -1 & -2\\
2 & p & p
\end{array}\right)\implies E_{31}E_{21}A=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}
